products.body_html: Nao proves that basics don’t have to be boring - because vest tops deserve high-quality craftsmanship.

products.title: Naya Technical Organza Halter Low Back Shirt Dress - Green
products.body_html:
The Naya Dress is a celebration of boldness and breezy sophistication. Designed with a relaxed, flowing silhouette, it features a halter neckline, collar, low back and a dramatic, voluminous skirt that moves beautifully with every step. Effortless, eye-catching, and full of life - Naya is made for making a statement.
To save 40% of fabric that would otherwise be wasted, we have chosen not to use placement print. This means that each dress will have a unique print pattern. We do this in an effort to be more sustainable, but we also think it’s more fun!

products.title: Isola Plunge Abstract Print Flared Drape Sleeve Dress
products.body_html:
The Isola Dress is designed to make you look like art itself. Crafted in a soft, flowing fabric that moves with grace and a painterly print in striking shades of purple, orange, and black, Isola is designed for those who want to express confidence and creativity in every step. Perfect for evenings to make your best memories in- our founder got engaged in this dress!
To save 40% of fabric that would otherwise be wasted, we have chosen not to use placement print. This means that each dress will have a unique print pattern. We do this in an effort to be more sustainable, but we also think it’s more fun!
Estimated dispatch will be from the 16/07/25

products.title: Rina Plunge Ruched Layered Ruffle Cotton Top - Yellow
products.body_html:
The Rina Top is all about bold femininity and effortless impact. Inspired by our highly coveted Adesuwa dresses, it features a deep flattering neckline, gathered waist, and a cascading peplum with soft ruffle layers that add playful movement to every step. Rina is the perfect piece to brighten up any outfit. Pair her with your Koa or Khala Denim for a more casual vibe, or with the Yumi Skirt to be the life of any party. 
Estimated dispatch will be from the 16/07/25

products.body_html: The Colette Dress is the epitome of modern romance. Designed with a flattering ruched bodice, it sculpts the upper body before flowing into a dramatic, tiered skirt. Each ruffle adds volume and movement, creating an effortlessly striking silhouette. Perfect for summer soirées, and bridal looks. This is definitely a main character moment.

products.title: Renua Striped Silky Shirt - Purple
products.body_html:
Our Renua shirt is cut from a gorgeous high twisted rayon viscose- one of the most expensive yarns on the market and certified sustainable by the FSC. The fiber is made entirely from natural sources. It is a classic but luxurious classic that can be worn for any occasion.

Tanatswa (5'7) is wearing a size XS. 
The Renua shirt fits true to size, with a relaxed fit and no stretch. 
100% viscose striped jacquard, in a silky texture. 
Wash at a maximum of 30 degrees.
Hang line to dry.Do not tumble dry.
Alternatively dry clean for optimum results.
Iron using a cool setting and do not bleach.

Rebecca is 5'10, a UK 18-20 and is wearing a size 3XL.

It is minimalist enough for the girl with classic style but not without the drama that KAI has come to be known for, always primarily serving the girl who is the centre of attention in every room she walks into.

Specialist clean only.
